### 1. 인증 코드 발송 (새 이메일로)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "verifytest01@test.com" }

### 2. 인증 코드 검증 (터미널에 redis-cli GET "email:verify:verifytest01@test.com" 치기)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/email/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "verifytest01@test.com", "code": "417863" }

### 3. 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "verifytest01@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!",
  "passwordConfirm": "Test1234!",
  "name": "검증테스트",
  "nickname": "verify01",
  "phone": "010-9999-0001"
}

### 4. 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "verifytest01@test.com", "password": "Test1234!" }

### 5. 내 정보 조회 → emailVerified: true 기대
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me

> {%
    client.test("신규 가입자도 emailVerified true", function () {
        client.assert(response.body.data.emailVerified === true,
            "기대 true, 실제 " + response.body.data.emailVerified);
    });
%}
